<p><strong>In person</strong></p>
<p>You can find me in the <a href="http://depts.washington.edu/anthweb/">Department of Anthropology</a> at the <a href="http://www.washington.edu/">University of Washington</a>. My office is <a href="http://www.washington.edu/newsroom/tour/denny.html">Denny</a> 117, at the basement level. You can see below roughly where that is, but <a href="http://bit.ly/Bens-UW-Office-Map">here</a> is a Google map showing more preciesly the location of my office, and <a href="http://www.washington.edu/home/maps/northcentral.html?DEN">here</a> is the UW&nbsp;campus map showing Denny Hall. If you're just dropping by, check my <a href="http://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=benmarwick%40gmail.com&amp;ctz=America/Los_Angeles">calendar</a> before coming to make sure I'm available.</p>
